Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…有  有  有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎!?  女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她正在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的!?  是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之總之  恭喜了  小新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意認同我們的交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很擔心昨晚都沒有睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把她介紹給姐姐  已經帶她過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意見她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎  那女孩已經來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還太早了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她性格很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  百百  來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  這就是我的女友百百
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好

